snippet.title: 12 Hours to Die - Official Trailer [Available Now]
snippet.description:
Six students find themselves trapped inside their school. They are offered only one way to escape: murder one of the other trapped students and get away with it within 12 hours.

Free download for Windows, Mac, and Linux computers.
https://westeford.itch.io/12hours
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1345080/12_Hours_to_Die/

Trailer Music by 369
http://www.369musiq.com/index.html
